name: Signature T'
description:
The soon to be iconic FSFYM Branded signature T features our unique bold graphic on a high quality American Apparel tee. The shirt is also tagged with an inner neck print of the logo.

The water based print design occupies the front of the unisex tshirts, which are available in XS (30), S (34), M (38), L (42) and XL (46). 

Orders can currently only be shipped within the UK.

Photography by www.charlottedart.co.uk

name: Failure By Design T'
description:
Another late night basement tee..

The water based print design occupies the front of the unisex tshirts, which are available in XS (30), S (34), M (38), L (42) and XL (46).
